snippet: At least 20 passengers suffered minor to moderate injuries on Monday when a tractor-trailer collided with an Amtrak train south of Hanford in the Central Valley, the authorities said.
abstract: Tractor-trailer collides with an Amtrak train in California's Central Valley, leaving at least 20 train passengers injured.
lead_paragraph: At least 20 passengers suffered minor to moderate injuries on Monday when a tractor-trailer collided with an Amtrak train south of Hanford in the Central Valley, the authorities said.
